1) Install Pinax and activate your virtualenv

2) Checkout django-newsroom pinax branch inside the virtualenv
    svn co https://django-newsroom.googlecode.com/svn/branches/pinax --username

3) Install DN requirements pip install -r requirements/external_apps.txt

4) Install caveats by hand (photologue-3.x and django-countries) according to
   django-newsroom/docs/install.txt

5) Make sure you have django trunk
    pip install -e svn+http://code.djangoproject.com/svn/django/trunk#egg=django-trunk
